main problem i have with using non non-instants is  i simply cant drain my mana fast enough to oom on even longer events, sometimes can just barly keep ahead of  harvest's mana regen unless i do something like ie and ec on procs. i have to mix in instants here and there just to keep my mana were it should be at. dpm and much more mana spent to the point its ahead of harvest's mana regen by 1/2, is way to go in making these nukes better.
                  
